trans-unit.source: Represents the exclusive C14N XML canonicalization transform for a digital signature as defined by the World Wide Web Consortium (W3C), without comments.
trans-unit.target: Representerar det exklusiva C14N XML-kanonikaliseringstransformering för en digital signatur som definierats av World Wide Web Consortium (W3C) utan kommentarer.

trans-unit.source: The XmlDsigExcC14NTransform class represents the exclusive C14N XML canonicalization transform without comments.
trans-unit.target: Klassen XmlDsigExcC14NTransform representerar exklusiv C14N XML-kanonikaliseringstransformering utan kommentarer.

trans-unit.source: This class is similar to the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlDsigC14NTransform> class, which allows a signer to create a digest using the canonical form of an XML document.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen liknar den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlDsigC14NTransform>klass, vilket gör att en undertecknare att skapa en sammanfattad med hjälp av den kanoniska formen av ett XML-dokument.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlDsigC14NTransform>

trans-unit.source: However, the XmlDsigExcC14NTransform class excludes ancestor context from a canonicalized subdocument.
trans-unit.target: Klassen XmlDsigExcC14NTransform utesluter dock överordnad kontexten från ett av kanoniserade underdokument.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlDsigC14NTransform> class when you need to canonicalize an XML subdocument so that it is independent from its XML context.
trans-unit.target: Använd den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlDsigC14NTransform>klassen när du behöver kanonisera XML för underdokument så att den är oberoende av dess XML-kontext.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlDsigC14NTransform>

trans-unit.source: For example, applications such as Web services that use signed XML within complex communication protocols often need to canonicalize XML in this manner.
trans-unit.target: Till exempel behöver program som webbtjänster som använder signerad XML i komplexa kommunikationsprotokoll ofta kanonisera XML på detta sätt.

trans-unit.source: Such applications often envelop XML within various dynamically constructed elements, which can substantially change the document and cause XML signature verification to fail.
trans-unit.target: Sådana program omger ofta XML inom olika dynamiskt konstruerade element, vilket avsevärt kan ändra dokumentet och orsaka verifiering av XML-signatur misslyckas.

trans-unit.source: The XmlDsigExcC14NTransform class solves this problem by excluding such ancestor context from the canonical subdocument.
trans-unit.target: Klassen XmlDsigExcC14NTransform löser detta problem genom att utesluta sådan överordnad kontexten från det kanoniska deldokumentet.

trans-unit.source: Typically, you do not create a new instance of a canonicalization transform class.
trans-unit.target: Normalt skapar du inte en ny instans av en kanonikaliseringen transform-klass.

trans-unit.source: To specify a canonicalization transform, pass the Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) that describes a transform to the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedInfo.CanonicalizationMethod%2A> property, which is accessible from the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.SignedInfo%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Om du vill ange en kanonikaliseringstransformering skickar den identifierare URI (Uniform Resource) som beskriver en transformering som ska den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedInfo.CanonicalizationMethod%2A>-egenskap som är tillgänglig från den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.SignedInfo%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.SignedInfo%2A> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedInfo.CanonicalizationMethod%2A>

trans-unit.source: To acquire a reference to the canonicalization transform, use the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedInfo.CanonicalizationMethodObject%2A> property, which is accessible from the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.SignedInfo%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Om du vill hämta en referens till kanonikaliseringstransformering använder den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedInfo.CanonicalizationMethodObject%2A>-egenskap som är tillgänglig från den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.SignedInfo%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.SignedInfo%2A> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedInfo.CanonicalizationMethodObject%2A>

trans-unit.source: You are required to create a new instance of a canonicalization transform class only when you want to manually hash an XML document or use your own canonicalization algorithm.
trans-unit.target: Du måste skapa en ny instans av en klass för auktorisering transformeringen endast när du manuellt vill hash-ett XML-dokument eller använda din egen kanoniseringsalgoritm.

trans-unit.source: The URI that describes the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlDsigExcC14NWithCommentsTransform> class is defined by the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.XmlDsigExcC14NWithCommentsTransformUrl> field.
trans-unit.target: Den URI som beskriver den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlDsigExcC14NWithCommentsTransform>klass definieras av den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.XmlDsigExcC14NWithCommentsTransformUrl>fält.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.XmlDsigExcC14NWithCommentsTransformUrl> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlDsigExcC14NWithCommentsTransform>

trans-unit.source: The URI that describes the XmlDsigExcC14NTransform class is defined by the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.XmlDsigExcC14NTransformUrl> field.
trans-unit.target: Den URI som beskriver XmlDsigExcC14NTransform klass definieras av den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.XmlDsigExcC14NTransformUrl>fält.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.XmlDsigExcC14NTransformUrl>

trans-unit.source: For more information about the exclusive C14N transform, see the XMLDSIG specification, which is available from the World Wide Web Consortium (W3C) at www.w3.org/TR/xmldsig-core/.
trans-unit.target: Mer information om exklusiva C14N transformeringen finns i specifikationen XMLDSIG som är tillgängliga från World Wide Web Consortium (W3C) på www.w3.org/TR/xmldsig-core/.

trans-unit.source: The canonicalization algorithm is defined in the W3C Canonical XML specification, which is available at www.w3.org/2001/10/xml-exc-c14n.
trans-unit.target: Kanoniseringsalgoritm har definierats i specifikationen W3C kanoniska XML som finns på www.w3.org/2001/10/xml-exc-c14n.
